The paper focuses on evaluating the quality of sentence representations obtained from different modalities, including language modeling and image features prediction, and their performance on tasks such as image retrieval and semantic textual similarity. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper also mentions multimodal machine translation, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
